          "type": "data",
          "data": {
            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h2 id=\"3-automatische-peakliste-und-manuelle-korrektur\">3. Automatische Peakliste und manuelle Korrektur</h2>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Kontrolliere die Zuordnung im Plot. Falls die automatische Peak-/J-Zuordnung nicht stimmt, kannst du unten eine eigene Tabelle einf\u00fcgen.</span>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Erwartete Spalten f\u00fcr manuelle Korrektur:</span>\n<div class=\"language-gdscript codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">branch</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"n\">J</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"n\">isotope</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"n\">wavenumber_cm</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"n\">sigma_cm</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"n\">height</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"n\">area</span>\n<span class=\"n\">P</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"n\">H35Cl</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"mf\">2860.12</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"mf\">0.29</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"mf\">0.123</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"mf\">0.456</span>\n<span class=\"n\">P</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"n\">H37Cl</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"mf\">2858.03</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"mf\">0.29</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"mf\">0.041</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"mf\">0.153</span>\n<span class=\"n\">R</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"n\">H35Cl</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"mf\">2904.50</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"mf\">0.29</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"mf\">0.120</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"mf\">0.450</span>\n<span class=\"n\">R</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"n\">H37Cl</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"mf\">2902.40</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"mf\">0.29</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"mf\">0.040</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"mf\">0.150</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Wenn das Feld leer bleibt, wird die automatische Tabelle verwendet.</span></span>"
